"reviewer-name\">zaydB</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">septembrie 1, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Although this plugin is great there are definite issues with formatting and creating content the exactly the way you want it to look. From the overall look to tiny details, a little more improvement needs to be done to help people that are new to web development and dont know html or css. Ultimately its heading in the right direction but it still needs a lot of work. Keep it UP!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great Plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jovyk\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/44371fe476393949141fc37ecae221ce?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/44371fe476393949141fc37ecae221ce?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jovyk\" class=\"reviewer-name\">jovyk</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">august 17, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">great and helpful plugin.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=