on <span class=\"review-date\">octombrie 18, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Been using Elementor for a while. Great functionality. Have not found any hiccups yet. Easy to use. Works well. Used to use WP Page Builder. But will likely build all sites on Elementor going forward. Love it!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Easy to use</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/aryanair\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/dbc7944be6c268be56cd129f224ec36d?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/dbc7944be6c268be56cd129f224ec36d?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/aryanair\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Arya <small>(aryanair)</small></a> on <span class=\"review-date\">octombrie 17, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Even as a beginner in web development, I felt it is easy to create a website using Elementor. There are many tutorials available in Youtube to clarify the doubts. The free version itself has lots of features to create a good looking website.  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Stunning</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dispuutfabras\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/582cecb5357a334bed19719dbde15046?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/582cecb5357a334bed19719dbde15046?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dispuutfabras\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Benjamin <small>(dispuutfabras)</small></a> on <span class=\"review-date\">octombrie 17, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Wow what a awesome way to build a website.\n\nLooks logical, works logical.\nStop making things difficult for yourself, Elementor helps you to create a great website!\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Worst quality plugin. elementor means only error and error.</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-emp